CORNHILL PEGS PREMIUMS

Cornhill Insurance is pegging premiums paid by its TravelCover
policyholders at 1994 rates (excluding Insurance Premium Tax).
Improved benefits include

* a three day premium rate for both UK (adults #6.00 and child #3.00)
and European travel (adult #9.00 and child #4.50)

* improved family premium rates with one child covered free in a party
of two adults and two children
* a five per cent premium discount for groups of 10 travellers.



