DISCOUNT OR TRANSFER ALLOWANCE

Countrywide Insurance Marketing has launched Countrywide Zurich, a new
household policy which offers either a #20 new business premium
discount or a transfer allowance up to #25 (using a voucher) if a
proposer faces a transfer fee when transferring from a building society
or bank.  Countrywide Zurich is underwritten by Zurich Insurance and
has discounts for age of property, policy excess and no claims (at
renewal).



