RHINE RE

The directors of Rhine Reinsurance Co Ltd, Basel, have approved an
increase in share capital by SF25m (US$21.6m) to SF105m.  The capital
increase is being funded by Rhine Re's major shareholder, Basler
Versicherungs-Ges (La Baloise), Basel, which has also taken over the
shares held by the Limmat Insurance Co Ltd, Zurich, and Patria Life
Insurance Co, Basel.  Baloise now owns 86.3% of Rhine Re.



