BERKSHIRE HATHAWAY/GEICO

Berkshire Hathaway Inc, Omaha NE, has completed the acquisition of all
the outstanding shares in GEICO Corp, Washington DC, it did not already
own in a previously announced transaction worth US$2.3bn.  Each
outstanding share of GEICO common stock (par value US$1)  was bought
for $70 in cash.



