WORLD CORPORATE INSURANCE REPORT via NewsNet
January 12, 1996

NU

Norwich Union Fire Insurance Society Ltd (NU), Norwich, has set up its
own direct sales operation following the successful completion of a
pilot exercise last year (WICR165/21).  Norwich Union Direct began
operations this week and aims to develop a portfolio of 1.25m motor and
household risks by the year 2000.



