TRYGG-HANSA BUYS SAMPO'S STAKE IN HANSA KINDLUSTUS

Trygg-Hansa AB has bought out Sampo Group's minority holding in jointly-
owned Estonian insurer Hansa Kindlustus, Tallinn.  In Latvia, Trygg-
Hansa appears to be going ahead with its planned commercial insurer in
Riga (WICR180/22).



