automobiles to be built by Tianjin Automotive Industrial.
     If the Chinese government approves a Toyota application to set
up a joint venture with Tianjing Automotive Industrial, the two
Toyota affiliates want to supply parts to be made by their new joint
ventures to Toyota's own joint venture with Tianjin Automotive too,
the pair said.
