of top management directors was greatly lowered with the reshuffle,
bringing in new wind and vitality into overall group management.''
     Chung Mong Hun, 47, the fifth-eldest son of the group founder
and chairman of Hyundai Electronics Co., was named as vice chairman
of the Hyundai group to support his elder brother.
